# Citation File Format for Skill-Enrichment
# 详细规范: https://citation-file-format.github.io/

cff-version: 1.2.0
message: >-
  If you use this skill in research, please cite BOTH this repository
  AND the original EmbodiSkill paper. The core methodology (4-type
  reflection framework, S = (S_body, S_app) structure, classification
  logic) is from the paper; this repository's contribution is the
  engineering implementation and domain transfer to Claude Code skills.
title: "丰容 (Skill Enrichment)"
type: software
license: MIT
repository-code: "https://github.com/z77orz/Skill-Enrichment"
url: "https://github.com/z77orz/Skill-Enrichment"
keywords:
  - claude-code
  - claude-ai
  - agent-skill
  - skill-reflection
  - procedural-task
  - self-evolution
  - embodied-skill
  - skill-aware
authors:
  - family-names: "z77orz"
    given-names: ""
    alias: "z77orz"
    affiliation: "Independent"
date-released: "2026-06-01"
version: "1.0.0"

