references:
  - type: software
    title: "丰容 / Skill Enrichment (formerly Skill-Aware Reflection — Claude Code skill, engineering port of EmbodiSkill)"
    authors:
      - alias: "z77orz"
    date-released: "2026-06-01"
    url: "https://github.com/z77orz/Skill-Enrichment"
    notes: >-
      An operationalization of EmbodiSkill (Ju et al., 2026, arXiv:2605.10332)
      for Claude Code agent skills. Includes a Graphviz decision tree,
      anti-patterns table, self-test checklist, and 6 original worked
      examples in the Claude Code toolchain. MIT licensed.
